text: You were pretty helpful back there, but I just can't get my nerves under control!
Oh? Well, if you have an idea, I'm all ears.

A renovation? Don't you humans usually charge for that? 
 Houses don't usually have much disposable income…
Wait, what!? You'll do it free of charge!?
Yes! Yes, please, I'd love that!

I don't understand why you'd go so far for a house 
 you just met, but… thanks.
So, you need to go get materials? I'll wait here then.
